@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Flight Control Operator" as FCO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Report Generation Thread" as ReportThread
participant ":Shared Memory" as SharedMemory
participant ":Final Simulation Report" as FinalReport

activate FCO

FCO -> System : Requests final simulation report

activate System
System --> System : Check if FCO is authenticated and authorized
System --> System : Validate selected simulation
System --> System : Check if simulation is in a final state

alt simulation is finished, failed or terminated

    System -> ReportThread : Request final report generation

    activate ReportThread

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read final simulation metadata and configuration
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Final metadata and configuration
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read final flight process statuses
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Final process statuses
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read complete aircraft position history
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Complete position history
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read safety violation events
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Safety violation events
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read environmental influence data
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Environmental influence data
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> SharedMemory : Read warnings and errors
    activate SharedMemory
    SharedMemory --> ReportThread : Warnings and errors
    deactivate SharedMemory

    ReportThread -> FinalReport : Compile final simulation report
    activate FinalReport
    FinalReport --> ReportThread : Final report compiled
    deactivate FinalReport

    ReportThread --> System : Final simulation report
    deactivate ReportThread

    System --> FCO : Display final simulation report

else simulation is still running

    System --> FCO : Display report unavailable until simulation ends

else simulation does not exist or cannot be reported

    System --> FCO : Display final report generation error

end

deactivate System
deactivate FCO

@enduml